# Anything containing real values for these patterns should never enter the repo.
# This is belt-and-suspenders; the actual sanitization happens by hand
# (or via the sister repo's sync-from-local.ps1 if you adopt that pattern).

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.vscode/
.idea/

# Local-only secret maps (mirror the sister repo's convention)
sync-secrets.local.json
sync-secrets*.json
*.local.json
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Any actual API keys someone forgot was here
openai_api.txt
api_keys.txt

# Vault contents (if a user clones this into a vault by accident, don't leak)
wiki/sources/
wiki/_attachments/
wiki/log.md
wiki/hot.md
wiki/index.md
wiki/meta/notes-graph.md
.raw/

# Per-session runtime
binding-*.json
*.ndjson
*.log
*.offset
*.pid
*.last
